    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Beceri",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/17/35428890/10316b5178d5109d597f415d6e7903dc_3449546821165401130.png",
                "id": "talent28844",
                "key": "Oceanborne",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Oceanborne"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>This character gains a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Tidecaller: Surf Embrace</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Prepare Skill: Wavestrider</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Tidecaller: Surf Embrace</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Status</span></p><p>The next time this character acts, they will immediately use the Skill <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Wavestrider</span>.</p><p>While preparing this Skill: Grant 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Shield </span>points to this character to which this is attached.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Wavestrider</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>(Prepare for 1 turn)</p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/17/35428890/32f8641a1f41763d29139a4b8a6a4971_3685229238314504566.png",
                "id": "talent85652",
                "key": "Tidecaller",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Tidecaller"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>, creates 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Thunderbeast's Targe</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Thunderbeast's Targe</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Combat Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">After your character uses a Normal Attack</span>: Deal 1 <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">When your character receives at least 3 DMG</span>: Decrease DMG taken by 1.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Duration (Rounds)</span>: 2</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/17/35428890/0cce59adfbce4cdc1347ce3556a6f15c_6479559325400300814.png",
                "id": "talent5006",
                "key": "Stormbreaker",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Stormbreaker"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Electro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 for this instance, the target is forcibly switched to the next character</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/16/35428890/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_8627392168556876833.png",
                "id": "talent55157",
                "key": "Electro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Electro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Prepare Skill</span></strong></p><p>Some Skills cannot be used directly. Instead, they need to be <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">prepared </span>over a certain number of turns. When it is a certain player's turn, and this player's active character is currently <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparing </span>a Skill, this player's turn will be skipped. If the Skill has finished being <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">prepared</span>, the character will directly use that Skill at this time. (Skills that require <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparing </span>cannot activated effects triggered by \"using a Skill\") Only active character can <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">prepare </span>Skills, and if an active character who is <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparing </span>a Skill gets switched off-field, their <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparation </span>will be interrupted.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Shield</span></strong></p><p>This Shield will be consumed to protect the character who equips it from DMG.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Duration (Rounds)</span></strong></p><p>Each time you reach the end of a Round, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds) </span>-1.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span> runs out.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/17/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_7888485867517486710.png",
                "id": "talent91231",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
